---
title: Warming Chicken Noodle Soup with Ditalini Pasta and Dill Croutons
description: Perfect antidote to cold weather and cold season, this gorgeous soup is so simple to pull together and is jammed with fresh flavour. We top it off with crispy croutons that soak up the broth and add even more comforting flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/warming-chicken-noodle-soup-973ab4b7.jpg
